47
00:04:24,010 --> 00:04:26,310
Strange mark?

48
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:31,910
Yes. There is a mark like something hit it from outside.

49
00:04:33,810 --> 00:04:35,910
But what?

50
00:04:35,910 --> 00:04:37,010
Inspector Megure!

51
00:04:38,010 --> 00:04:41,310
