00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:39,710
What time is it now?

94
00:06:39,710 --> 00:06:41,010
What?

95
00:06:41,010 --> 00:06:43,910
What time is it now?

96
00:06:43,910 --> 00:06:45,610
What time...

97
00:06:45,610 --> 00:06:47,910
It's 8.00 pm.

98
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:51,210
