114
00:07:31,610 --> 00:07:33,210
What? Tokyo!

115
00:07:33,210 --> 00:07:34,710
Oh, yeah, that's right.

116
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:36,010
I was going to get back to you

117
00:07:36,010 --> 00:07:38,010
